{"author":{"id":"556161c50e4dc8dad8fbbd002e471363f574da2316e0a8e1878a577451694cd9"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1459524488,"nonce":"f1R5fdJ9vSGJQVK9Z4W7Ng+YHf4=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDU6SXNzdWUxNDUyMTAxODA=","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/700","origin":"github"},"title":"IUC Codefest - Conda dependencies","message":"On monday 04/04, @bgruening and some members of Galaxy team (me and @nitesh1989 at least) would want to get a Codefest on adding IUC / Devteam tools Conda dependencies.\n\nHackathon begins at: 10am (UTC-4) / 4pm (UTC+2).\n\nHangout link: https://hangouts.google.com/call/xp6vucjka5bj7pq53uoohol6zie\n\nIt will be as following:\n- [x] @bgruening will give a small introduction how to create a recipe and the scripts involved in it]\n- [x] Introduce everyone to conda and bioconda\n- [x] Then we pick a simple tool and create it\n- [x] @bgruening will provide a list with bugs that needs to be fixed on the framework level\n\nAims:\n- get familiar with conda packaging the conda-Galaxy integration\n- remove tools from the testing blacklists: [1](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/blob/master/.tt_blacklist) [2](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-devteam/blob/master/.tt_blacklist) [3](https://github.com/bgruening/galaxytools/blob/master/.tt_blacklist)\n- Integrate Travis-conda testing in GalaxyP\n- Integrate Travis-conda testing in galaxy_blast (@peterjc?)\n\nInfrastructure work:\n- https://github.com/galaxyproject/galaxy/issues/2047\n- condarc is update if you add new channels, but you can not remove channels\n- conda is not working in the Galaxy Docker image\n- bioconda needs to archive all tarballs to depot.galaxyproject.org\n- Galaxy Admin support to remove environments\n\nTools to convert (for beginners):\n- [ ] raxml\n- [ ] vegan\n- [x] seqtk\n- [ ] bcftools - [WIP Tools-IUC #707 ](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/pull/707)\n- [ ] art - [WIP Tools-IUC #709](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/pull/709)\n- [ ] macs2 - [WIP Tools-IUC #710](https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/pull/710)\n- [ ] diamond\n- [ ] crossmap - https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/pull/702\n- [ ] STAR-Fusion - https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/pull/704\n\nConda packages to create (for beginners):\n- [ ] PileOMeth (C/C++)\n- [x] bamhash - [WIP BioConda Recipes #1196](https://github.com/bioconda/bioconda-recipes/pull/1196)\n- [ ] openms\n- [ ] imagej2 (Java)\n- [x] find_subsequences =\u003e Biopython is available in [Conda](https://anaconda.org/search?q=biopython), see https://github.com/bgruening/galaxytools/pull/329 \n- [ ] all tools under tools/rna_tools/ (C/C++)\n\nLet us know if you are interested!","files":null}]}